Docs.summary: This class and its members are reserved for internal use and are not intended to be used in your code.

remarks.para: Each PSDBField member is a field in one or more of the datasets that are used in PSI methods. The fields also generally correspond to fields in the Draft, Published, and Archive databases for Project Server. Those databases are not documented.
